类 PrefixKeyDeltaEncoder

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    DataBlockEncoder

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class PrefixKeyDeltaEncoder
extends BufferedDataBlockEncoder
    Compress key by storing size of common prefix with previous KeyValue and storing raw size of rest. Format: 1-5 bytes: compressed key length minus prefix (7-bit encoding) 1-5 bytes: compressed value length (7-bit encoding) 1-3 bytes: compressed length of common key prefix ... bytes: rest of key (including timestamp) ... bytes: value In a worst case compressed KeyValue will be three bytes longer than original.

      • getFirstKeyCellInBlock

        public Cell getFirstKeyCellInBlock(ByteBuff block)
        从接口复制的说明: DataBlockEncoder
        Return first key in block as a cell. Useful for indexing. Typically does not make a deep copy but returns a buffer wrapping a segment of the actual block's byte array. This is because the first key in block is usually stored unencoded.
        参数:
        block - encoded block we want index, the position will not change
        返回:
        First key in block as a cell.
